values:
Yea...it has been a while since I updated, but I needed to get this off my chest.

This birthday has been the worst. First, my parents wanted me home on my birthday so I had to rush packing and going to my doctors appointment and then drive the two hours to cypress. Because of all this CRAP I had to take care of, I forgot to register for summer classes. Yes...big fucking oops. So now I'm stuck taking a Physics class at 8 in the fucking morning at northridge. Where the FUCK is northridge you ask??? It's about 23 fucking minutes.

So I get home expected to at least spend time with my family since my parents (DAD) wanted me home. NO such deal. Mom had to work. Cherry was at work. DAD gets home and forgets that it's my birthday. THANKS SO MUCH DAD!

Next day (today) my dad bitches at me for only taking fourteen hours this semester....let's see daddy dearest....I had six hours of FUCKING lab a week and three science class plus American Dilemmas which was a worthless piece of shit class. 

I'm exhausted. I'm so tired of these expectations. I don't want to go to med school anymore. All this crap...I just don't know if it's worth it anymore. I mean, yes, I would love to be a doctor and all and save some lives while I'm at it, but getting there is just so hard and it's not making me happy. I don't know what to do with life anymore, because I'm tired of it. I'm tired of everything and I just want to be done with it and just sleep forever.

On the twelfth day of Christmas, christi_gale sent to me...
Twelve massages drumming
Eleven pandas piping
Ten earrings a-reading
Nine christmas baking
Eight starbucks a-procrastinating
Seven blankets a-shopping
Six movies eating
Five cla-a-a-assic movies
Four random quotes
Three french movies
Two green eyes
...and a winter in a fauxbritboi.
Get your own Twelve Days:
gee i haven't updated in a long time..did you miss me?? lots of things happened this year..... biggest change???? i got bangs. other things: now a bio major, tested positive for tb (yea that was fun), quit which wich? (technically I just disappeared), now a tutor.

My left cheek is the size of a fucking golf ball because I had to get another wisdom tooth out. FUCK the wisdom teeth!!!!! I don't understand why they grow to annoy the hell out of people so they fucking look like the fucking Michelin marshmellow man the next day...and guess what people...this girl did not get a fucking IV or fucking laughing gas...and guess again.. this girl LOVES the gas!!! and they wouldn't even give me that...no they just give me a bunch of shots to numb my poor mouth and when it's too late to back out the dentist dude tells me that he's going to make an incision on my gums that's going to cut through effing bone and I'm going to need stiches right afterwards of course he tells me while he has the damn scapel shoved in my mouth....and who doesn't get a fucking script for the meds??? ME...o pop some advil he says..well FUCK that!!!!!

And what the hell is up with TV!!!! I barely watched TV and now I'm ADDICTED to it...so sorry college, my schedule has to revolve around my daytime soaps and homework as to take a backseat because of primetime TV...it's that and of course tell Which Wich I can't come back because I can't work during Gilmore Girls or OTH...sorry...I want TiVo...

BTW, I am going to a Vietnamese Buddhist temple in approximately 5 hours...why??? for a project for summer school. so I called the place and they were like come over at 10:30...so if I come back all in tuned with my Zen ....blame stupid school.

Adriane and Nicki: What happened to Belle Black??? I used to love her..hell I used to like Sammy but that girl just needs to hook up with EJ or someone because Austin isn't worth it!!!!!!! I used to hate Mimi because she was like the biggest biatch in the whole world and I hate that new girl..whatsherface...she killed JT and is Beaus daughter with another woman besides faith...ehh..need to go to sleep

Miss you guys..

Happy Birthday Cilla!!!

Yes adriane i did get your call...thanks for the reminder..i was driving down to beaumont when i got your call..sorry..anyways


HAPPY BIRTHDAY HARRY POTTER!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
i can't believe it..chad michael murray is engaged to an 18 year old...what happened to sophia..she's hot...chad michael murray. you used to be the love of my life but no more!

okay so i'm getting my wisdom teeth surgically removed tomorrow, it's finally happening after 2 years of bugging my dentist. anyways, there's no visible vein on my arm.......i can't find one. where are they going to stick the iv because they're not getting anywhere near my wrist...freaking out here.

well, i actually sent a request tranfer for the university of pennsylvania, but that's still up in the air so no worries yet.

new obsession, gilmore girls. actually it was an old one brought back to life

found my soul mate...HALF PRICE BOOKS how i love thee. you and me together forever.

i will love you forever if someone builds me a bookcase....

actually, the fam and i are coming down to the apartment on tax free weekend so i can move in all my stuff and buy stuff i need..so dixie, adriane, and nicki...get ready for some pino craziness cause the whole family is coming down...

So I'm taking this Intro to World Religions class..and it's fun. I have to go to a service other than a Christian one, specifically a Catholic mass. I'm thinking of going to a Buddhist meditation service...I get to meditate in a garden and eat a free vegetarian lunch..LEELA..if you're reading this, do you want to come with?? Sorry to the people who have tried to call my cell. I just refuse to answer it. Don't know why. Not angry or mad or anything..I'm just in a funky mood. Weird. Miss you all!!

Gale's creature-nemesis:

The Dreaded LORAX
'What creature will become your nemesis?' at QuizGalaxy.com

1. Leave me a comment saying, "Interview me."
2. I will respond by asking you five questions of a very intimate and creepily personal nature. Or not so creepy/personal.
3. You WILL update your LJ with the answers to the questions.
4. You will include this explanation and an offer to interview someone else in the post.
5. When others comment asking to be interviewed, you will ask them five questions.


1. what is your happiest memory from childhood?

       My favorite memory from childhood was fishing trips with the best friends. They were so much fun. I remember always catching next to nothing and Caroline and Charisse making fun of me. The place we fished at was called Pleasure Island and there was a big playground there and we always camped out. Oh and once I thought I saw a mermaid...it was awesome!

2. what were the best and worst things about cheerleading?

      The best thing about cheerleading was stunting and the friends. I was a base but that was my favorite thing to do. Our uniforms were cute but i think i was allergic to the pom poms....i always itched right after we used them. The worst thing about cheerleading.....the early morning practices...we had to run 4 times around the track which equaled a mile and run up stairs which was scary. Also we did this thing called stations and it was a bunch of different exercises and I hated v-ups which is the worst sort of sit up. I got hurt alot because I had girls falling on me almost every practice....

3. what are your top 5 favorite bands?

      This is in no particular order: Say Anything, Maroon 5, Dave Matthews, Death Cab, Eisley...I don't know...it's all I can think of off the top of my head...o..I really like Saves the Day 


4. what is your favorite book?

      This is probably the hardest thing, umm....Ella Enchanted, Harry Potter, the Narnia Series..all these are from my childhood..and I absolutely adore fairy tales, there's probably so much more because I read a lot...the Philip Pullman books are really good to and so was the Redwall Series...now I really like Kafka, and Austen, Pride and Prejudice though is probably my all time favorite book...and most of the classics I've read I really like Salinger, Fitzgerald, Hemmingway, the Bronte sisters, Oscar Wilde, Shakespeare...this was a bad question...lol

5. what is your usual morning routine?

     Now that Nicki's my room mate???? She tries to wake me up everymorning....I sleep until the absolute latest time, I usually shower at night, sometimes in the morning, brush my teeth, do my hair (it takes me two minutes if I leave it curly and 30 if I straighten it), then make-up, and then get dressed. So I take about thirty minutes to get ready since I like to take my time... LOL...

1) I did not have my glasses...so I got a warning.
2) My license did not have the right address...so I got a second warning.
3) My insurance expired yesterday...so I got my third warning...
4) I was going 86 on a 65....so I got a ticket.....

O well...I miss everyone.
